terms.title: External Attribution
terms.Text: The process of assigning the cause of behavior to some situation or event outside a person's control rather than to some internal characteristic.

terms.title: Internal Attribution
terms.Text: The process of assigning the cause of behavior to some internal characteristic, rather than to outside forces.
